                            <path d="M11 6C11 5.72386 10.7761 5.5 10.5 5.5C10.2239 5.5 10 5.72386 10 6V12C10 12.2761 10.2239 12.5 10.5 12.5C10.7761 12.5 11 12.2761 11 12V6Z" fill="black" />
